 all we can to keep <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disruption_of_1843" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disruption_of_1843" target="_blank">disruption</a> as a result of the work to a minimum and motorists can keep up to date with real time traffic information by visiting the Traffic Scotland website and following their Twitter feed&quotAdvanced warning signs will also be in place to inform motorists that work is underway&quot
